            "id": 6169136,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 櫃買市場加權指數下跌-5.65點至257.48點，跌幅2.15%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間26日10:58，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌5.65點（或2.15%），暫報257.48點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.26%</li><li>近 1 月：+6.32%</li><li>近 3 月：+12.85%</li><li>近 6 月：+4.61%</li><li>今年以來：+2.85%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>車用記憶體概念領跌-4.22%。其中    宜鼎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5289-TW</a>)            下跌        7.45%            ;        南亞科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)            下跌        6.27%            ;        力旺(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3529:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3529\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3529-TW</a>)            下跌        4.79%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>18吋晶圓概念領跌-3.85%。其中    盟立(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2464:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2464\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2464-TW</a>)            下跌        6.03%            ;        辛耘(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3583:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3583\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3583-TW</a>)            下跌        4.94%            ;        中砂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1560:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1560\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1560-TW</a>)            下跌        3.68%    。</p></section></main>",
